<body><div class=WordSection1>
<div class="brand">📚 ENGLISH CODING · 영어코딩</div>
<h1>🧩 M002 Extension 2 — Piston &amp; Logic Maze</h1>
<p><strong>Topic:</strong> Two Pistons + AND · <strong>Course:</strong> Maze Madness · <strong>Level:</strong> Extension (Beginner) · <strong>Time:</strong> about 30 minutes</p>
<p>The agent walks a <strong>redstone trail</strong> and flips a <strong>lever</strong> to open a <strong>piston</strong> gate. Get it to the end.</p>
<hr />
<h2>1 · Chat Words 🎛️</h2>
<p>A word makes the agent move.</p>
<pre><code>type &quot;r&quot;:
    turn right
</code></pre>
<p><strong>You type <code>r</code>. Circle one:</strong> turn left · turn right · jump</p>
<pre><code>type &quot;rl&quot;:
    come back to you
</code></pre>
<p><strong>You type <code>rl</code>. Circle one:</strong> to the goal · back to you · nowhere</p>
<hr />
<h2>2 · AND means BOTH 🔍</h2>
<p><strong>AND</strong> is true only when <strong>both</strong> are true.</p>
<pre><code>if redstone left AND redstone ahead:
    turn left
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Redstone is left, but NOT ahead. Turn left? Circle one:</strong> yes · no</p>
<p><strong>Redstone is left AND ahead. Turn left? Circle one:</strong> yes · no</p>
<hr />
<h2>3 · Fill the Gap ✏️</h2>
<p>Turn left only when <strong>both</strong> are true.</p>
<pre><code>if redstone left ____ redstone ahead:
    turn left
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Missing word? Circle one:</strong> AND · OR</p>
<hr />
<h2>4 · Show Your Work 📸🎥</h2>
<p>Open <strong>M002 EXT 2</strong> and type <code>run</code>. Reach the end past both pistons; if it sticks, run again.</p>
<p>Record <strong>one video</strong> — one take, no stopping (a phone is fine). Show these in order:</p>
<p><strong>1 · Your code.</strong> Scroll through it. Say what each part does.</p>
<p><strong>2 · Your build.</strong> Point the camera. Name the parts.</p>
<p>Say these out loud, filling in the blanks:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Today I built ______.</p>
<p>I built it using this code: ______.</p>
<p>In this code I used ______.</p>
<p>The hardest part was ______.</p>
<p>That part was hard because ______.</p>
<p>The most fun part was ______.</p>
<p>Something new I learned was ______.</p>
</blockquote>
<hr />
<h3>Submit ✅</h3>
<p>Send this worksheet + your video to teacher on KakaoTalk.</p>
<div class="footer">영어코딩 · <b>english-coding.co.uk</b></div>
</div></body></html>
